hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I stay at home and look after the children nolvadex gdje kupiti But in the mid-16th century, writing music had nothing to do with “expressing oneself”. It was about crystallising a particular moment in life, such as a dance, a wedding or a particular liturgy in church. In Palestrina, the “crystallising” is done in the purest way, by gilding it in beauty. His aim was to take the smooth polyphonic vocal style he’d inherited from the great Flemish composers, and make it perfect.
